<title>ạ̉tʿb ktyr wạḥzn ktyr</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ạ̉tʿb ktyr wạḥzn ktyr .. lmạ ạ̉kẖtạr lnfsy ṭryqy wfyh ạ̉syr
 ạ̉tʿb ktyr wạḥzn ktyr .. lmạ fy buʿdy bạ̹ydy ạ̉ḥfr ạ̉lf byr)2
 wạnsy̱ klạm qlth ktyr .. ạ̹n ạ̹nt drby wḥdk (wmʿạk ạlmṣyr)2
 ạlqrạr- (mḥtạj lṣwtk .. mḥtạj rʿạytk
 mḥtạj tqwl ly .. ạ̉nạ ḥạss bḥyrtk)2
 trsẖdny myn .. wtqwl ly fyn
 tmskny ydk ạ̹nt .. (mn ạ̹ydy ạlymyn)2
 2- (ạ̉frḥ ktyr wạbqy̱ bṣyr .. lmạ msẖwrtk tbqy̱ nwry fy ạlmsyr
 wạnsy̱ ạlậlạm wạnsy̱ ạlmlạm .. lmạ ạ̉lạqy fy ạlly ạkẖtrth kl kẖyr)2
 wạ̹n nạdạny ạlbʿd tạny .. ạ̉ḥrsny mn ḍʿfy (wmn myly ạlḍryr)2</lyrics>
</song>